      <title>由於利息收入疲軟，PNC 利潤下降 21%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pnc-profit-falls-21-amid-weaker-interest-income-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PNC Financial Services 週二公佈第一季利潤下降 21%，因為該銀行在高利率環境下為持有客戶存款支付了更多費用，導致利息收入下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pnc-profit-falls-21-amid-weaker-interest-income-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
